  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Culture centre of St. Vincent Palotti</narrative>
   <narrative xml:lang="SK">Kult&#xFA;rne centrum sv. Vincenta Palotti</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="SK">Hlavn&#xFD;m cie&#x13E;om projektu je zlep&#x161;enie pr&#xED;stupu k pred&#x161;kolsk&#xE9;mu vzdelaniu v oblasti Kibeho. Celkov&#xFD; cie&#x13E; bude dosiahnut&#xFD; prostredn&#xED;ctvom zjednodu&#x161;enia dostupnosti vzdelania pre deti z najchudobnej&#x161;&#xED;ch rod&#xED;n. Okrem pred&#x161;kolskej pr&#xED;pravy je cie&#x13E;om centra aj zv&#xFD;&#x161;enie kvality a nutri&#x10D;nej hodnoty stravy, najm&#xE4; pre podvy&#x17E;iven&#xE9; deti, predch&#xE1;dzanie chorob&#xE1;m a identifik&#xE1;cia individu&#xE1;lnych potrieb det&#xED; z oblasti Kibeho. Dobrovo&#x13E;n&#xED;k sa bude spolupodie&#x13E;a&#x165; na koordinovan&#xED; aktiv&#xED;t centra, bude spolupracova&#x165; s miestnou komunitou pallot&#xED;nov a anim&#xE1;tormi, bude tr&#xE1;vi&#x165; &#x10D;as s de&#x165;mi a bude dohliada&#x165; na finan&#x10D;n&#xE9; z&#xE1;le&#x17E;itosti centra. Rovnako bude distribuova&#x165; nutri&#x10D;n&#xFA; stravu podvy&#x17E;iven&#xFD;m de&#x165;om mimo projektu kult&#xFA;rneho centra a koordinova&#x165; v&#xFD;stavbu novej budovy &#x161;k&#xF4;lky pre v&#xE4;&#x10D;&#x161;&#xED; po&#x10D;et det&#xED;.</narrative>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Main goal of the project is to improve access to pre-school education in the Kibeho region. Goal will be achieved by simplifying access to education for children from the poorest families. Besides pre-school preparation the centre aims to improve quality and nutritional value of the food, especially for under-nourished children, prevention against diseases and identification of individual needs of children in the Kibeho region. Volunteer will take part in co-ordination activities of the centre, he/she will co-operate with local community of the Pallotines and tutors, spend time with the children and supervise financial issues of the centre. He/she will also distribute nutritional food to the under-nourished children beyond the project of the culture centre and co-ordinate construction of a new kindergarten building for a larger ammount of children.</narrative>
  </description>
